HyperBrowse Portable Build

This folder contains the portable HyperBrowse layout for Windows 10/11 x64.

Contents:
- HyperBrowse.exe
- Any Microsoft Visual C++ runtime DLLs staged by CMake for this toolchain
@HYPERBROWSE_PORTABLE_NVIDIA_CONTENT_LINE@
- RUNTIME-DEPENDENCIES.txt

Run:
1. Keep all files in this folder together.
2. Launch HyperBrowse.exe.
3. Open a folder from File > Open Folder or press Ctrl+O.

Notes:
- User settings are stored in HKCU\Software\HyperBrowse.
- @HYPERBROWSE_PORTABLE_NVIDIA_RUNTIME_LINE@
- No installer is required for this layout.